result.title: Not able to submit on codeforces
result.content: Hello Everyone, I am trying to submit problems here, but unfortunately i am not able to submit. When i click the submit button, the page keeps connecting/loading and i am not redirected to any page and finally "Page not found" message is printed on the screen ! I am trying from last 2 days but not able to submit any problems ! Please anyone help me resolving the issue ! I have tried using the different browser as well but that does'nt works too ! All other pages are working fine on codeforces but only "submit page is not working" ! Thanks !
